🛣️ Three-Lane Mobility Model

Space DMV assumes three mobility domains:

Lane	Authority	Examples	
Ground	State DMV	Cars, motorcycles, autonomous pods	
Air	FAA	Drones, eVTOL, small aircraft	
Space	Space DMV	Hybrid craft, shuttles, orbital vehicles	


Space DMV focuses on Lane 3 and the bridges between lanes.

---

🔗 Interoperability Model

DMV → Space DMV

• Verify state ID
• Verify ground license class
• Read-only


FAAO → Space DMV

• Verify pilot certificate
• Verify airworthiness class
• Read-only


Space DMV → DMV/FAA

• Provide DVV verification
• Never writes to government systems


